Saurin karuwa a cikin cututtukan kamuwa da cutar coronavirus (COVID-19) a cikin EU / EEA da UK daga 1 ga Janairu zuwa 15 ga Maris, 2020
Ƙaruwar cutar coronavirus (COVID-19) tana nuna irin wannan yanayin a cikin ƙasashen EU / EEA, kuma Burtaniya ta tabbatar da cewa yayin da suke cikin matakai daban-daban dangane da kowace ƙasa, annobar COVID-19 tana ci gaba da sauri a cikin dukkan ƙasashe.
Dangane da kwarewar Italiya, ƙasashe, asibitoci da cibiyoyin kulawa ya kamata su haɓaka shirye-shirye don karuwar marasa lafiya na COVID-19 waɗanda za su buƙaci kulawa ta likita, musamman kulawa mai tsanani.
A ranar 31 ga watan Disamba, 2019, an samu rahoton wani mutum da ke fama da cutar sankarar bargo, wanda ba a san asalin cutar ba, a Wuhan, lardin Hubei, China.
A ranar 9 ga watan Janairun 2020, Cibiyar Kula da Cututtuka da Cututtuka ta kasar Sin ta ba da rahoton cewa wani sabon nau'in coronavirus ne mai dauke da kwayar cutar coronavirus ta 2 na cutar sankarar barkwanci mai saurin yaduwa (SARS-CoV-2).
Tun daga wannan lokacin, cutar da ke haifar da kamuwa da cutar SARS-CoV-2 an sanya mata suna Coronavirus (COVID-19).
Shaidar da aka samu ya zuwa yanzu ita ce kashi 80% na mutanen da ke fama da COVID-19 suna da cutar mai saurin kamuwa da cuta ta hanyar numfashi tare da ko ba tare da cutar huhu ba, kuma yawancin waɗannan marasa lafiya sun warke.
A cikin kashi 14 cikin ɗari na COVID-19, cutar ta ci gaba zuwa mawuyacin hali wanda ke buƙatar asibiti, yayin da kashi 6 cikin ɗari ke da mummunan yanayin da ke buƙatar kulawa mai tsanani.
Yawan mutuwar marasa lafiya da aka sallama daga asibiti saboda COVID-19 ya kai kashi 4%.
A cikin wannan binciken, mun kimanta yanayin karuwar cututtukan COVID-19 a kowace ƙasa ta EU / EEA da Burtaniya kuma mun kwatanta su da lardin Hubei na China.
Mun kuma kwatanta yawan adadin masu kamuwa da cutar COVID-19 a cikin ƙasashen EU/EEA da Ingila da adadin masu kamuwa da cutar a Italiya a lokacin 31 ga Janairu zuwa 15 ga Maris, 2020.
Cutar COVID-19 a cikin ƙasashen EU / EEA da United Kingdom.
Bayan da cutar ta mamaye China, COVID-19 ta ci gaba da yaduwa, kuma annobar COVID-19 mai saurin yaduwa a duniya a halin yanzu tana bin hanyar China.
A ranar 11 ga Maris, 2020, Darakta Janar na Hukumar Lafiya ta Duniya (WHO) ya ayyana COVID-19 a matsayin cutar ta duniya.
A cikin fitowar 5th na Eurosurveillance 2020, Spiteri da sauransu sun ba da rahoton farkon yanayin COVID-19 da Turai ta tabbatar bisa ga ƙididdigar cutar ta WHO.
A cikin Turai / Yankin Tattalin Arziki na Turai, an fara tabbatar da wasu mutane uku da Faransa ta bayar da rahoto a ranar 24 ga Janairun 2020 ga mutanen da suka dawo daga Wuhan, lardin Hubei, China.
A ranar 15 ga Maris, 2020, an gano wasu cututtukan COVID-19 a cikin ƙasashe 30 na Tarayyar Turai / Yankin Tattalin Arzikin Turai da Ingila, waɗanda a tsakanin 31 ga Disamba, 2019, kuma a wannan ranar, an sami adadin kamuwa da cutar 39,768, kuma an ba da rahoton mutuwar 1,727, wanda 17,750 daga cikin kamuwa da cutar da 1,441 daga cikin mutuwar ya fito ne daga Italiya kadai.
An karɓi jimlar lambobi da kuma abubuwan da ke faruwa a cikin kwararar adadin masu cutar COVID-19.
A Cibiyar Kula da Cututtuka da Cututtuka ta Turai (ECDC), ana sabunta adadin adadin COVID-19 da aka ruwaito a kowace ƙasa a duniya, wanda aka samu daga kafofin hukuma kamar ma'aikatun kiwon lafiya, hukumomin kiwon lafiya na ƙasa da na yanki, da Hukumar Lafiya ta Duniya, kowace rana da ƙarfe 8:00.
Duk waɗannan bayanan an yi amfani da su don kimanta cutar COVID-19 a cikin ƙasashen EU / EEA da UK kuma an kwatanta su da na Italiya.
A matsayin wakilci na barkewar cutar COVID-19, mun lissafa jerin abubuwan da suka faru na cutar COVID-19 da suka daidaita a cikin kwanaki 14, la'akari da yanayin cutar COVID-19 a cikin kowace ƙasa ta Tarayyar Turai / Yankin Tattalin Arzikin Turai (EU / EEA) da Ingila daga 1 ga Janairu zuwa 15 ga Maris, 2020.
Mun kuma nuna karuwar adadin masu kamuwa da cutar a kowace kasa da aka ruwaito a ranar 15 ga Maris, 2020 da karfe 8:00 na safe, idan aka kwatanta da Italiya a lokacin 31 ga Janairu zuwa 15 ga Maris, 2020.
Yanayin COVID-19 a cikin ƙasashen Turai / Yankin Tattalin Arziki na Turai da Ingila
Yanayin a cikin COVID-19 wanda ke gudana a cikin kwanaki 14 a cikin EU / EEA da Burtaniya yana bin hanyar da aka samu a lardin Hubei (China) (Hoto na 1).
Ga EU / EEA da kuma duk Burtaniya, yawan kamuwa da cutar COVID-19 ya fara tashi a ranar 21 ga Fabrairu, sannan ya karu sosai a ranar 28 ga Fabrairu, 2020 (ƙarin bayani).
Wannan galibi ana haifar da saurin karuwar adadin shari'o'in da aka ruwaito daga Italiya, amma ƙasashen Turai / Yankin Tattalin Arzikin Turai da Burtaniya sun nuna irin wannan karuwar karuwar abubuwan da ke faruwa na COVID-19 (ƙarin bayani).
Hoto na 2 ya nuna jimlar adadin masu kamuwa da cutar COVID-19 a cikin ƙasashen Turai / EEA da Ingila idan aka kwatanta da Italiya a cikin 31 ga Janairu zuwa 15 ga Maris, 2020.
Rahoton ya nuna cewa a ranar 15 ga Maris da karfe 8:00 na safe, sauran ƙasashe 15 na EU / EEA da Ingila sun ba da rahoton ƙananan adadin masu cutar, idan aka kwatanta da adadin masu cutar a Italiya, wanda ya kasance makonni 3 da suka gabata ko ƙasa da haka.
Sakamakonmu ya nuna cewa adadin adadin masu cutar COVID-19 da aka ruwaito suna ƙaruwa cikin sauri a cikin ƙasashen EU/European Economic Area da United Kingdom.
Abubuwan da aka lura a cikin yanayin COVID-19 sun nuna cewa cutar ta ci gaba a kusan kowane yanki.
Wannan ya bambanta da ƙasashe a matakai daban-daban, canje-canje a cikin amsar lafiyar jama'a na ƙasa da ƙididdigar shari'ar ƙasa, da kuma hanyoyin da za a zaɓi marasa lafiya don yin gwaji don tabbatar da cutar COVID-19, gami da gwaji.
A farkon Maris 2020, likitoci a yankunan da suka fi fama da cutar a Italiya sun ba da rahoton halin da ake ciki a yankin cewa kashi 10 cikin ɗari na marasa lafiyar COVID-19 suna buƙatar kulawa mai mahimmanci, kuma kafofin watsa labarai da yawa sun ba da rahoton cewa asibitoci da sassan kulawa mai tsanani a yankunan suna aiki da mafi kyawun ƙarfin su.
Bayanai kan karɓar COVID-19 a asibitoci da/ko cibiyoyin kulawa mai tsanani a halin yanzu suna samuwa a matakin EU/ASAR don kashi 6% da 1% na shari'o'i, bi da bi (ba a nuna bayanai ba).
Koyaya, yakamata a tattara su ta hanyar tsari don haɓaka bayanan sa ido na yanzu wanda ke mai da hankali kan adadin shari'o'in da aka ruwaito da yawan mutuwar.
Nazarin da aka gudanar a 201011 ya nuna babban canji a cikin yiwuwar samar da kulawa mai mahimmanci da matsakaicin matsakaiciyar kulawa a Turai, wanda ya fito daga gado 29.2 a Jamus zuwa gadaje 4.2 a cikin mazauna 100,000 a Portugal.
Wannan yana nufin cewa ƙasashe na iya samun ƙarin ko ƙasa da albarkatu fiye da Italiya (ƙididdigar 12.5 na matsakaitan kulawa da gadaje na matsakaici ga mutane 100,000 a 2010-11).
An ba da samfurin yanayin da ya shafi rashin lafiyar lafiya a cikin sabon sabon tsarin kimantawa na mata na shida daga COVID-19 na ECDC, tare da kimantawa ga ƙasashen EU / EEA da UK cewa yawan masu karɓar COVID-19 yana da haɗari fiye da ƙarfin samar da gadaje masu kulawa da gaske &gt; 90%.
Saboda yawancin lokuta suna faruwa a cikin yankuna a cikin ƙasashen Turai, Yankin Tattalin Arziki na Turai da Ingila, kuma asibitoci da cibiyoyin kulawa da hankali suna ba da sabis ne kawai ga yawan jama'ar yankin da aka ƙayyade, saboda haka ya kamata a ba da bayanin lokuta da tsarin kulawa a kan sunan yanki na yanki don ƙididdigar 2 (NUTS-2).
Kwarewar Italiya da halin da ake ciki a wasu ƙasashe ya nuna cewa annobar COVID-19 ta duniya tana ci gaba cikin sauri a cikin ƙasashen EU/EEA da Ingila.
Saboda haka, ƙasashe, asibitoci da cibiyoyin kulawa ya kamata su kula da shirye-shirye don sabon yanayin watsawa ga al'umma na SARS-CoV-2 wanda zai iya zama mai yaduwa da kuma karuwar yawan marasa lafiyar COVID-19 da ke buƙatar kulawa ta musamman da kulawa ta musamman, kamar yadda lamarin yake a yankunan da ke fama da cutar a Italiya.
Kamar yadda aka nuna a cikin sabon kimantawa na haɗarin ECDC, hanzari, dacewa, da kuma cikakkiyar hanyar amsawa suna da mahimmanci don jinkirta yaduwar cutar SARS-COV-2, ta hanyar sauyawa daga rigakafi zuwa ragewa, yayin da saurin karuwar lamuran na iya ba masu yanke shawara da asibitoci isasshen lokaci don fahimta, yarda da amsawa idan ba a aiwatar da su da wuri ba.
Aikin kimanta haɗarin da sauri ya haɗa da matakan kiwon lafiyar jama'a don rage tasirin cutar.
Akwai ɗan gajeren lokaci a lokacin da ƙasashe ke iya ƙara haɓaka ayyukan gudanarwa don rage yaduwar SARS-CoV-2 da rage matsin lamba ga cibiyoyin kiwon lafiya.
Idan ba a yi hakan ba, tsarin kiwon lafiya na EU / sauran ƙasashen Turai na iya fuskantar karuwar marasa lafiya da ke buƙatar kulawa mai mahimmanci a cikin kwanaki ko makonni masu zuwa.
