Kwayar cutar ta yi kama da kwayar cutar da ke da halaye na musamman, SARS-CoV, wanda ya haifar da cutar SARS a cikin dubban mutane a 2003. SARS-CoV-2 na iya yaduwa daga beraye kuma yana haifar da alamun bayyanar cututtuka ta hanyar aiki kamar SARS-CoV.
Koyaya, COVID-19 yana da ƙananan mawuyacin hali da ƙananan mutuwar fiye da SARS, amma yana da saurin yaduwa kuma yana shafar tsofaffi fiye da matasa, kuma maza sun fi kamuwa da cutar fiye da mata.
Don amsawa ga yawan wallafe-wallafen da ke ci gaba a kan wannan cuta mai yaduwa, wannan labarin yana so ya ba da cikakken bayani game da wani bincike mai sauri.
Za mu tattauna game da asali na cututtukan cututtuka, abubuwan da ke haifar da su, ilimin cututtuka, ganewar asali, magani, tsinkaya da rigakafin cututtuka.
Kodayake akwai tambayoyi da yawa da ba a amsa ba, muna fatan wannan nazarin zai taimaka mana mu fahimci kuma mu kawar da wannan barazanar.
Bikin bazara a ranar 25 ga Janairun 2020 ya zama abin da ba a taɓa gani ba kuma ba za a iya mantawa da shi ba ga duk Sinawa waɗanda aka ƙarfafa su su zauna a gida duk lokacin hutu da kuma makonni bayan barkewar sabon cutar.
Wannan kwayar cutar ta yi kama da kwayar cutar coronavirus (CoV) wacce ta haifar da barkewar cutar sankarar barbashi mai saurin kamuwa da cuta (SARS) a 2003. Saboda haka, an sanya mata suna SARS-CoV-2 ta Hukumar Lafiya ta Duniya (WHO) a ranar 11 ga Fabrairu, 2020, kuma an sanya wa sauran cututtukan da ke da alaƙa suna CoV Disease-19 (COVID-19).
Cutar ta fara ne a Wuhan, China, inda ta bazu cikin sauri a cikin gida da kuma zuwa kusan ƙasashe 50 a duniya.
Ya zuwa ranar 2 ga Maris, 2020, kwayar cutar ta haifar da kamuwa da cutar COVID-19 80000, tare da sakin marasa lafiya sama da 40,000 daga asibiti, da mutuwar marasa lafiya sama da 3000.
Hukumar Lafiya ta Duniya ta yi gargadin cewa COVID-19 shine babban magabcin jama'a kuma yana da ƙarfi fiye da ta'addanci.
A cewar PubMed (https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/), a cikin ƙasa da watanni biyu, an buga nazarin bincike sama da 200 game da cutar COVID-19, gami da nazarin kwayar cutar, kamuwa da cuta, ganewar asali, da magani tun lokacin da aka fara bayar da rahoto a ranar 7 ga Janairu, 2020, wanda ya tsara jerin ƙwayoyin cuta waɗanda ke keɓewa daga marasa lafiya da yawa.
Wannan bita yana ƙoƙari ya taƙaita ci gaban bincike a cikin sabbin fannoni masu tasowa cikin sauri.
A duk lokacin da zai yiwu, za mu yi ƙoƙarin kwatanta COVID-19 da SARS, wata cuta da kwayar cutar coronavirus (CoV) ke haifarwa, wato, cutar MERS (wanda ta ɓarke a shekarar 2012).
Za mu kuma tattauna abin da muka koya game da rigakafi da hasashen cututtuka da kuma tambayoyin da muke buƙatar amsawa cikin gaggawa.
Yawancin lokaci, ana ɗaukar CoVs a matsayin masu haifar da cutar da ba ta da haɗari ga ɗan adam, yawancinsu suna haifar da cutar mura, kusan kashi 15% na cutar mura 4.
Koyaya, a cikin wannan karni, mun sami wasu ƙananan cututtukan coronavirus (CoVs) waɗanda ke haifar da cututtukan mutane sau biyu, SARS-CoV da MERS-CoV, waɗanda suka haifar da barkewar farko a China a 2003 da Saudi Arabia a 2012, sannan suka bazu zuwa wasu ƙasashe da yawa tare da mummunan yanayi da yawan mutuwa.
Saboda haka, a halin yanzu COVID-19 shine barkewar kwayar cutar coronavirus (CoV) ta uku a tarihin ɗan adam.
Kamar yadda aka nuna a hoto na 1.1., an fara bayar da rahoton wani kwararar cutar sankarar bargo daga birnin Wuhan a ranar 31 ga watan Disamba, 2019 zuwa Hukumar Lafiya ta Kasa ta kasar Sin.
Bayan kwana bakwai, an saki jerin sunayen cututtukan coronavirus (CoV).
A ranar 15 ga Janairun 2020, an ba da rahoton mutuwar farko daga Wuhan.
A halin yanzu, annobar ta yadu cikin sauri zuwa garuruwan da ke makwabtaka da shi, larduna da ƙasashe.
A ranar 20 ga Janairu, an ba da rahoton kamuwa da cututtukan masu ba da kiwon lafiya, wanda ke nuna cewa yaduwar mutum zuwa mutum na iya faruwa.
A ranar 23 ga watan Janairu, an rufe birnin Wuhan ba tare da sufuri na jama'a ba.
A ranar 24 ga Janairu, binciken farko na gwaji na cutar ya nuna cewa daga cikin marasa lafiya 41 da suka kamu da cutar, 21 ne kawai ke da alaƙa kai tsaye da kasuwar kayan abincin teku ta Wuhan, wanda ake tsammanin ya haifar da kamuwa da cuta daga dabbobi da ba a sani ba.
A ranar 30 ga Janairu, Hukumar Lafiya ta Duniya ta ayyana cutar a matsayin gaggawa ta kiwon lafiya a duniya.
A lokacin da wannan rahoto ya fito, cutar ta yadu a duk faɗin China da kusan wasu ƙasashe 50 a duniya (Figure 2).2)
