Koyaya, ingancin alluran rigakafin rayuwa, waɗanda ke yin waɗannan gwaje-gwajen a cikin tsofaffi da samfuran haɗari, da kariyar su daga kamuwa da kwayar cutar genotoxic (dabba zuwa mutum) dole ne a ƙayyade kafin a fara nazarin gwaji na zahiri.
Wannan na iya zama saboda cutar SARS ta sake barkewa shekaru 17 da suka gabata kuma ba a sami rahoton sabbin mutane ba.
A gefe guda, wasu cututtukan cututtukan cututtuka da cututtukan cututtukan MERS sun ci gaba da faruwa a Gabas ta Tsakiya kuma sun bazu zuwa wasu yankuna saboda rashin iyawar asalin genotoxic (dabba zuwa mutum) a cikin yankunan da ke fama da cutar.
An haɓaka dabarun samar da allurar rigakafi don MERS ta amfani da ƙwayoyin cuta marasa aiki, DNA plasmids, masu ɗaukar hoto, nanoparticles, ƙwayoyin cuta masu kama da ƙwayoyin cuta da kuma ɓangarorin furotin da aka sake haɗawa, kuma an gwada wasu dabarun don gwadawa da kimantawa a kan dabbobi.
Ci gaban allurar rigakafi mai inganci da aminci ga SARS-CoV-2 ga mutanen da ba su da rigakafi yana da gaggawa da mahimmanci don hana cutar.
Koyaya, har yanzu yana da matsala wajen shawo kan wannan mawuyacin halin saboda tsayi mai tsawo (gabaɗaya watanni 18) da ake buƙata don haɓaka allurar rigakafi da saurin maye gurbin CoVs.
A matsayin sabon nau'in cutar, COVID-19 yana fara bayyana a cikin gwaji lokacin da akwai dubban marasa lafiya.
