Matsalolin damuwa: Kamar yadda aka bayyana a sama, a lokacin barkewar cutar COVID-19, yawancin marasa lafiya sun sami damuwa ta musamman saboda suna jimrewa da rashin kwanciyar hankali, rashin tabbas, da kuma ganin mutuwar danginsu da sauran marasa lafiya.
Yana da mahimmanci a ba da shawara na hankali da tallafi na dogon lokaci don taimakawa waɗannan marasa lafiya su rabu da damuwa da komawa rayuwa ta yau da kullun.
Dangane da binciken alƙaluma na baya, COVID-19 ya bayyana ya bambanta da cutar SARS.
Baya ga yaduwa a cikin ƙananan hanyoyin numfashi, SARS-CoV-2 yana iya yaduwa ta hanyar hanyoyin numfashi na sama yadda ya kamata kuma yana haifar da alamomi ko rashin alamomi a farkon lokacin kamuwa da cutar, wanda yayi kama da sauran coronaviruses, wanda ke haifar da mura na yau da kullun.
Saboda haka, marasa lafiya da ke kamuwa da cutar a farkon lokaci ko kuma a lokacin da ba su nuna alamun cutar ba na iya samar da kwayoyin cuta masu yawa yayin ayyukan yau da kullun, wanda ke haifar da wahalar sarrafa cutar.
Koyaya, ana ɗaukar ci gaba ko watsawa na SARS-CoV a matsayin lokacin da marasa lafiya ke da mummunan yanayi, yayin da yawancin kamuwa da cuta ba su faru a farkon matakin ba.
Saboda haka, barkewar cutar COVID-19 ta yanzu ta fi barkewar cutar SARS tsanani da wahala.
A halin yanzu, ana ci gaba da yin gagarumin ƙoƙari a China, gami da rufe Wuhan da kewayenta da kuma keɓewar kusan dukkanin jama'a, da fatan zai iya hana ci gaba da yaduwar cutar SARS-CoV-2.
Duk da cewa waɗannan ayyukan sun lalata tattalin arzikin ƙasar da sauran fannoni, yawan sabbin masu cutar yana raguwa, wanda ke nuna raguwar yaduwar cutar.
A mafi yawan lokaci, ana tsammanin cewa barkewar cutar za ta ƙare a watan Maris, kuma lokacin raguwa zai kasance tsakanin watanni 3-4.
Duk da haka, wasu masana ba su da irin wannan ra'ayi.
