A watan Disamba na 2019, sabon coronavirus na 2019 (2019-nCoV) ya haifar da barkewar cutar, wanda yanzu aka sanya wa suna a hukumance cutar coronavirus ta 2019 (COVID-19), kuma an sanya wa wannan cutar suna mai tsanani na cututtukan numfashi mai tsanani wanda ake kira coronavirus 2 (SARS-CoV-2).
A ranar 11 ga Maris, 2020, Hukumar Lafiya ta Duniya ta ayyana COVID-19 a matsayin annoba.
Don yaƙar kamuwa da cutar SARS-CoV-2, ƙungiyarmu ta haɓaka jagororin gaggawa kuma an buga su akan layi a cikin binciken likitancin soja a ranar 06 ga Fabrairu, 2020.
Ya jawo hankali sosai tun lokacin da aka buga shi.
Koyaya, lura cewa COVID-19 sabuwar cuta ce, fahimtarmu da iliminmu suna ƙaruwa koyaushe bisa ga binciken da ke gudana da ƙwarewar aikin asibiti, don haka ana sabunta dabarun bincike da magani koyaushe.
Misali, Shawarwarin kan ganewar asali da magani na COVID-19 da Hukumar Kiwon Lafiya ta Jama'ar Jamhuriyar Sin ta bayar (Janairu 16, 2020 zuwa Maris 3, 2020) ta fitar da sanarwa, jimlar wallafe-wallafe bakwai, wasu daga cikin abubuwan da suka shafi sun canza sosai.
Yanzu, shawarwarinmu sun sami amsa daga Zhou et al. Sun ba da shawarar yin amfani da ƙididdiga masu sauƙi bisa ga kwarewarsu ta asibiti.
Aikin su ya kara sabon shaida ga manufofinmu kuma ya zama babban takaddar tarihi ga cutar a duk duniya.
Muna goyon bayan muhimman ayyukansu kuma muna godiya.
Amma aikin su yana buƙatar sabuntawa dangane da sabbin jagororin bincike da magani na COVID-19 (na bakwai) da kuma sabbin karatu.
A cewar bugu na bakwai (Maris 3, 2020), don tabbatar da yanayin rashin tabbas, ya zama dole a haɗa kowane abu na tarihin cutar da abubuwa biyu na bayyanar cututtuka don yin cikakken bincike, ko kuma buƙatar cika alamun bayyanar cututtuka uku idan tarihin cutar bai bayyana ba:
Tarihin cutar: (1) Tarihin tafiya ko zama a Wuhan da kewayenta ko wasu al'ummomin da aka bayar da rahoton cutar COVID-19 a cikin kwanaki 14 da suka gabata kafin bayyanar cututtuka; (2) Tarihin hulɗa tare da cutar SARS-CoV-2 (tare da gwajin kwayar cutar nucleic acid mai kyau); (3) Tarihin hulɗa tare da mai zazzabi ko mai cutar numfashi daga Wuhan da kewayenta ko wasu al'ummomin da aka bayar da rahoton cutar COVID-19 a cikin kwanaki 14 da suka gabata kafin bayyanar cututtuka; (4) Tarihin haɗuwa da hanci (≥ 2 lokuta na zafi / zafi da alamun kamuwa da cuta ko ya faru a cikin makonni 2, a cikin ƙananan wurare, da dai sauransu).
Bayyanar alamun asibiti: (1) zazzabi da / ko cututtukan na numfashi; (2) tare da bayyanar cututtuka na COVID-19; (3) yawan adadin jini yana nuna raguwa na al'ada ko rage yawan ƙwayoyin cuta a farkon farawa.
Gano cutar ya kamata ya dogara ne akan yanayin da ake zargi tare da kowane abu mai cutarwa ko kuma waɗannan shaidu masu zuwa: (1) gwajin PCR na lokaci mai kyau don SARS-CoV-2 (2) jerin kwayoyin halittar gaba ɗaya, ƙwayoyin cuta suna nuna babban kama da sanannun coronaviruses (3) tabbatacce ga takamaiman IgM antigen da IgG antigen ga SARS-CoV-2 a cikin sake gwadawa na jini ko canzawar takamaiman antigen na SARS-CoV-2 daga mara kyau zuwa ko inganta IgG sau ≥ 4 a cikin farfadowa da fata wanda yake a cikin matakin farko na gwaji.
Za mu iya ganin cewa an haɗa gwajin polymerase chain reaction don nucleic acid a cikin ƙwayar cuta ko jini a cikin bugu na biyu (Janairu 18, 2020) da na uku (Janairu 22, 2020).
An gabatar da gano abubuwan da ke haifar da cututtuka na jini a cikin bugu na huɗu (Janairu 27, 2020) da na biyar (Fabrairu 8, 2020), sannan an gabatar da shaidar daga nazarin jini a cikin bugu na bakwai.
Waɗannan canje-canjen sun dogara ne akan masu bincike suna ci gaba da aiki don nemo mafi kyawun kayan aikin gano nucleic acid don saurin ganewar asali, da kuma samfurin daga hanyoyin numfashi, gami da ɗaukar jini, wanda ke haɓaka wadatar samfuran daban-daban da taimakawa haifar da sakamako mai kyau na ƙwayoyin cuta zuwa yanayin kamuwa da cuta.
Bugu da ƙari, akwai ƙarin shaidu da ke gargaɗe mu mu yi taka tsantsan da marasa lafiya da ke da alamun rashin lafiya da ba su da alamun cutar.
Don haka, ya kamata a sabunta jadawalin Zhou et al. saboda sun ɗauki mutane ba tare da alamun asibiti ba a matsayin masu ƙarancin haɗari.
Hakanan ana buƙatar tsarin ƙididdiga don ƙarin aiki da nazarin asibiti.
A ƙarshe, muna fatan ƙarin shaidar kai tsaye ta zo kuma muna kira ga masu karatu su ba da ra'ayoyinsu.
Don yin bincike na cutar da ake zargi da cutar, muna ba da shawarar bin sabbin ka'idojin ƙasarsu.
Ƙungiyarmu za ta sabunta shawarwarinmu a kan lokaci don ba da taimako.
Bangladesh ta ba da rahoton sabbin mutuwar COVID-19 guda biyar, mafi girma a kowace rana
A jiya, Bangladesh ta tabbatar da sabbin mutuwar biyar daga COVID-19 a ranar.
Wannan shi ne adadin mutane da suka mutu a rana guda daga cutar.
Kamar yadda yake a jiya, Cibiyar Kula da Kula da Cututtuka da Kula da Cututtuka ta Bangladesh (IEDCR) ta ba da rahoton cewa adadin adadin masu kamuwa da cutar da aka rubuta sun hada da masu aiki 114 da kuma 33 da suka warke da ke zama a gida.
