Darakta na Hukumar Lafiya ta Duniya Tedros Adhanom ya ce PHEIC na da matukar hadari saboda yaduwar cutar a duniya, musamman ga kasashe masu karamin karfi da matsakaitan karfi da ba su da ingantaccen tsarin kiwon lafiya.
"A cikin martani ga aiwatar da takunkumin hana tafiye-tafiye, Tedros ya bayyana cewa ""babu wani dalili ga matakan da ke hana balaguron kasa da kasa da cinikayya ba dole ba"" da kuma cewa ""WHO ba ta ba da shawarar ƙuntatawa da sauya wuraren ba"."
"A ranar 5 ga Fabrairu, Hukumar Lafiya ta Duniya ta yi kira ga al'ummar duniya don bayar da gudummawar dala miliyan 675 don samar da kudade don shirye-shiryen dabaru a cikin ƙasashe masu ƙarancin kuɗi, daga gaggawa don tallafawa waɗancan ƙasashe waɗanda ba su da tsarin gano mutanen da ke da kwayar cutar, duk da cewa hakan na faruwa. """
"Tedros ya ci gaba da yin jawabi, yana mai cewa ""duk al'umma idan akwai wanda ya raunana, to duk sun zama marasa lafiya"" kuma ya bukaci al'ummar duniya da su ""sanya jari a yau, ba tare da rasa abubuwa da yawa ba daga baya"."A wani taron manema labarai a ranar 11 ga Fabrairu, Hukumar Lafiya ta Duniya ta ba da sunan cutar COVID-19".
A ranar, Tedros ya tabbatar da cewa Sakatare Janar na Majalisar Dinkin Duniya António Guterres ya amince da bai wa dukkan tsarin Majalisar Dinkin Duniya ikon amsawa.
"An kafa rukunin kula da rikicin Majalisar Dinkin Duniya, wanda hakan zai ba da damar daidaitawa ga duk amsoshin Majalisar Dinkin Duniya, wanda zai ba WHO damar mai da hankali kan amsar kiwon lafiya yayin da sauran hukumomin za su iya kawo ƙwarewar su don tallafawa zamantakewar tattalin arziki da tasirin ci gaban barkewar cutar""".
A ranar 14 ga watan Fabrairun da ya gabata, an kafa kungiyar WHO tare da kasar Sin don samar da kwararru na duniya da WHO game da halin da ake ciki a kasar Sin don taimakawa wajen kula da cutar a cikin gida da kuma tantance "tsananin cutar da kuma yiwuwar yaduwar cutar", ta hanyar kafa bita da tarurruka tare da manyan cibiyoyin kasa da kasa, da kuma gudanar da ziyara ta musamman don fahimtar tasirin matakan amsawa a lardin da na yanki, gami da cibiyoyin da yankuna.A ranar 25 ga Fabrairu, WHO ta sanar da cewa ya kamata duniya ta dauki matakai da yawa don shirya wa cutar coronavirus, kamar yadda ta kira a cikin gaggawa, duk kasashen duniya su kasance cikin shiri.
Don mayar da martani ga yaduwar barkewar cutar a Iran, Hukumar Lafiya ta Duniya ta tura wani hadin gwiwa a can don tantance halin da ake ciki.A ranar 28 ga Fabrairu, jami'an Hukumar Lafiya ta Duniya sun ce za a kara kimanta barazanar coronavirus a duniya daga  mai matukar girma, wanda shine mafi girman matakin tsaro da kimantawa.
Mike Ryan, darektan shirin gaggawa na WHO, ya yi karin haske a cikin wata sanarwa cewa: "Wannan gwaji ne na gaskiya ga kowace gwamnati a duniya: farka".
"Wannan kwayar cutar na iya kasancewa a kan hanyarsa, don haka kuna buƙatar ku kasance cikin shiri, kuna ba da shawarar cewa matakan da suka dace na iya taimakawa duniya kauce wa mafi munin sakamako"."
"Ryan ya ci gaba da cewa, "babu tabbacin da aka samu na yanzu don jami'an kiwon lafiya su ayyana yaduwar cutar a duniya, yana mai cewa irin wannan sanarwar za ta nuna cewa ""mun amince da cewa kowa a duniya zai kamu da cutar""".
A ranar 11 ga Maris, Hukumar Lafiya ta Duniya ta sanar da barkewar cutar coronavirus.
Darakta ya ce WHO ta damu matuka da irin yanayin da ake ciki na barkewar cutar da kuma tsananin da ake ciki da kuma rashin daukar mataki.WHO ta fuskanci suka da dama saboda rashin ganin an yi wani mataki mai inganci kan cutar, ciki har da bayyana dokar ta baci ta kiwon lafiya da kuma sanya kwayar cutar a matsayin wata annoba.
Amsar ta hada da takardar neman izinin Tedros Adhanom, Darakta Janar na Hukumar Lafiya ta Duniya, don neman ya yi murabus daga mukaminsa, wanda mutane 733,000 suka sanya hannu a ranar 6 ga Afrilu.
