Sauran nau'ikan kayan aikin numfashi na iya ba da ƙarin kariya da haɓaka ƙwarewar ma'aikata. WHO ba ta ba da shawarar saka riguna masu sutura ba, saboda COVID-19 cuta ce ta numfashi maimakon watsawa ta hanyar ruwa.
Hukumar Lafiya ta Duniya ta ba da shawarar cewa a sanya abin rufe fuska na tiyata ga ma'aikatan da ke kula da shigarwa.
Ga waɗanda ke karɓar samfurin numfashi, masu kulawa, ko masu jigilar marasa lafiya na COVID-19 ba tare da hanyoyin samar da iska ba, WHO ta ba da shawarar yin amfani da abin rufe fuska, rigar ido, ko abin rufe fuska, riguna da gashin hannu.
An yi amfani da hanyar da za a iya yin amfani da shi don yin amfani da kayan aiki mai mahimmanci ko na ruwa zuwa gas, an maye gurbin masks na N95 ko FFP2.
Saboda wadatar PPE a duniya ba ta isa ba, WHO ta ba da shawarar rage buƙatun PPE ta hanyar telemedicine, ta hanyar amfani da kayan aiki na jiki kamar windows, ba da damar masu kula da kai tsaye su shiga ɗakunan da ke dauke da marasa lafiya na COVID-19 kawai, suna amfani da PPE da ake buƙata don takamaiman aiki, ci gaba da amfani da na'urar numfashi iri ɗaya ba tare da cire shi ba yayin kula da marasa lafiya da yawa tare da ganewar asali iri ɗaya, saka idanu da daidaita layin samar da PPE, da kuma ƙarfafa amfani da shinge ga mutane marasa alamun bayyanar cutar.
