ACE2 kuma yana iya kashe wasu peptides, ciki har da [des-Arg9] - bradykinin, apelin, neurotensin, dynorphin A, da ghrelin.
ACE2 yana taimakawa wajen daidaita matakan watsawa na SLC6A19 da kuma C-amino acid masu aiki a cikin cutar Hartnup.
Saboda haka, ACE2 yana aiki a matsayin babban hanyar shiga cikin kwayar halitta don wasu ƙwayoyin cuta, ciki har da HCoV-NL63; SARS-CoV (wanda ke haifar da SARS) da SARS-CoV-2 (wanda ke haifar da COVID-19).
Mafi mahimmanci, jujjuyawar kwayar S1 na SARS-CoV da SARS-CoV2 zuwa enzyme ACE2 wanda ke kan farfajiyar kwayar halitta, sakamakon rarrabuwa da kuma kawar da wuri na kwayar cutar da kuma shigar da enzyme cikin endosomes a cikin kwayar halitta.
